Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: NEO smart contract for StreamDesk was developed by Streamity team. The team had taken into account all the functional and non-functional requirements during the development. NEO smart contract allows to block the currencies NEO, GAS inside StreamDesk system, with the subsequent unlocking and sending to the address in NEO network. The smart contract has functions of storing the status of transactions and blocking tokens at its address in NEO network. The transactions structure in a smart contract has a status, a buyer, a seller and a commission, with the ability to lock tokens until it is needed to transfer them to the buyer’s address or to the seller’s address in case of a transaction cancellation.  This means that you can buy / sell not just Ethereum for fiat money but also NEO and GAS at Streamdesk platform, absolutely quickly and safely.  When selling NEO, a commission is taken in GAS, but a buyer does not pay the commission when he buys NEO. It means that a seller should have GAS in the wallet.  Why does Streamity choose NEO  In our opinion, NEO surpasses Ethereum in several parameters:  - NEO transaction speed is 1000 times faster than Ethereum. - GAS and NEO separation. There are huge advantages of using two different tokens when working with PoS protocol. - Low transactions commissions. NEO smart contract at StreamDesk is developed in such a way that we don’t charge any commissions for operations with NEO. It means that it is possible to use our platform with no commission, even with no commission in GAS - NEO can not produce fork which is an important parameter for being accepted by a real world economy. - NEO supports many encoding languages. - NEO has a more efficient and faster way to fulfil smart contracts than Ethereum.  “I consider that NEO has much more opportunities for growth and development than Ethereum. Now we can see the influx of ICOs and applications being developed on the basis of NEO. And this trend will just grow further. And as this trend grows, a need for NEO and GAS will grow with it. So now it is easy to exchange NEO and GAS for fiat using StreamDesk platform.  It is important to add that Chinese market which is about 1,4 billion people has not been mastered yet. Just imagine the excitement around NEO platform after removing ICO and cryptocurrency restrictions in China, as China prefers to use its own products and business innovations. One of NEO’s benefits is that the platform is aimed to meet regulatory requirements for the platform suitable for a smart economy. Thus, we can confidently say that adding NEO and GAS into StreamDesk is Streamity’s first step to the Chinese market development.”  Vladislav Kuznetsov, CEO Streamity Streamity team’s plans for the near future  In addition to NEO and GAS, in September we plan to launch a decentralized Bitcoin trade in an absolutely innovative way, with the help of a smart contract of another blockchain. Also the team has already begun to develop atomic transactions between NEO and Ethereum networks, but we will tell you about it a little later.  And we are glad to inform you that we are going to launch our first course for cryptotraders , which incorporated all the most important and necessary information for people who want to successfully start crypto trading.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: We have analyzed the p2p platforms and dexchanges! Found their weak places  - in the secure sector mostly, difficulty in access  for avafage users! Lack of curriensies and super high fees! We are trying count all the risks! (Even legislation) we work with cryptocurrency - it is locked in our smart contract, and fiat is transferred within the payment systems, but we integrate API of the payment system with the smart contract, what I mean is that they interact with ech other (the smart contract receives a signal from the API of a payment system as one account receives fiat money from another account). It is very similar to Local Bitcoins, but the security is guaranteed thanks to the process described above. And most important thing is that payment systems will have official contracts with us, since everything is legal, we receive API data easily and officially, which means that we have created a completely legal service and we do not violate the laws of different jurisdictions.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: 💥 STREAMITY ICO has completed   Dear investors and all those who believed in our project during all this time!   Together with you we have passed a long and difficult path of several months. Our goal is to create an educational portal in the field of blockchain, where Streamity will help beginner crypto investors find their bearings in the world of digital money.  There users will be able to get recommendations and forecasts for successful crypto investing. The concept of the website can be summed up in one phrase: "the entire cryptocurrency market in one place". Here you will find first-hand information and news, analytics, discussions... The functionality will cover a lot yet stay easy to use!  The website will not only feature Streamity's own research articles, but from other players on the cryptocurrency market since we want to create a relevant and useful portal.  Users' questions will be answered by active investors and traders who have gone through more than one price crash and know how to share their knowledge in the field of finance and cryptocurrency trading. The roster will also include experts on blockchain, law and marketing with extensive experience in the ICO business, authors of investment articles and videos.  https://streamity.org

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: 📌 Why STREAMITY is going to Asia?   According to the statistics of Bitnovosti portal, up to 70% of fees in ICO projects are provided by investors from China and other Asian countries. This is the region where three-quarters of all new bitcoins of the world are mined (according to Liao Xiang, the head of Lightningasic). And miners are willing to invest coins in interesting ICO projects. In China people are particularly interested in any technological innovation and we just had to tell them about our project and show them STREAMDESK platform.   The team of STREAMITY has already convinced of the loyalty and engagement of Asian potential investors! On July 21 and 22, as a part of our Asian crypto tour, we already held the first meetings with the community and received a feedback. We have seen from our own experience that personal meetings of the project team with Chinese investors give an excellent result!   As Tony Ling, the co - founder of BitBlock Capital Fund (over $100 million investment in ICO), said- there are several million retail investors in China. Going on an Asian crypto tour, we expect to interest those who want to meet us and learn more about STREAMITY!   We remind you that the ICO of the project will be completed on August 6, 2018 and until this moment we will have time to visit Beijing and Shanghai! Follow the news in our social networks!  https://streamity.org

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: 📌 We would like to tell you more about Vladislav Kuznetsov, the CEO of Streamity!  He is a cryptocurrency, fintech and blockchain expert and cryptocurrency investor! In addition, he is an experienced businessman!  For the past 8 years Mr. Kuznetsov was actively interested in Blockchain technology and cryptocurrencies. He started developing his interest in traditional finance back in 2003, for the next 8 years he had multiple mentors and educated himself in the sphere of  financial markets. Vladislav became a successful trader - in less than a year he earned his first million.  Later Vladislav Kuznetsov began working with cryptocurrency. He was able to assess the prospects and become an investor in projects such as EOS, Waves, æternity and Monaco.  What happened when a fintech specialist started working with cryptocurrencies?  Vladislav personally saw all the problems of the market and understood what traders and investors need. So was created the idea of Streamity.  This project is derived from analyzing and observing or the clash of two different banking systems. Streamity project is powered by StreamDesk that is the first ever decentralized platform for exchanging payments for any currency, which allows users to trade without intermediaries.  Mr. Kuznetsov and our team have initiated ICO, during its Pre-sale the project raised 5 Million. Streamity Project is dedicated to help billions of people who are facing the above-mentioned challenges!  🔺If you have questions to Vladislav - ask them in the comments and get an answer!  https://streamity.org

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: 📌 In the coming years the number of cryptocurrency users will grow by 60 times   CTO of cryptocurrency exchange Coinbase, Balaji Srinivasan, is sure that in the near future the number of cryptocurrency holders will catch up the number of those who use smartphones. The growth in this area can be about 6000%. He cites the following statistics: in the world less than 1% of population own cryptocurrency and 63% have smartphones. At the same time, today a huge number of people already know about the digital economy and digital assets, and  developers of applications for mobile devices are actively integrating functions of buying or selling cryptocurrencies. Thus, smartphone becomes kind of a door to the crypto world.  Srinivasan made his prediction based on the results of a research conducted by Finder among 2000 thousand Americans. Its results showed that about 8% of Americans own cryptocurrencies, and in the whole world this figure is below 1%. At the same time, users who are not ready to buy cryptocurrencies in the near future admitted that they simply do not feel the need for digital currencies, are afraid of high risks, frequent fraud and difficulties in the process of buying and selling.  Streamity also believes that cryptocurrencies will gain popularity. Right now you can learn how our project simplifies the process of buying / selling cryptocurrency and increases the level of transactions' security on our website https://streamity.org

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: ♨️ ICO of STREAMITY project is gaining momentum!  💢 There are only 17 days left until the end of the tokensale, and we've decided to tell you about the benefits of our STM tokens!  🔺 Streamity token (STM) is the internal currency of our project and it means that payment for all services of the project will be accepted only in STM. We expect that after the launch of the platform, the number of its users will be constantly growing - this will be promoted by the convenience of STREAMDESK, favorable rate, transparency... And the more users are - the higher will be the demand for STM tokens, because the increase in demand always leads to an increase in the token rate!  ☑️ Some more important facts about STM tokens:  ▪️ Credit/debit of traditional money to exchanges will be more profitable through STREAMDESK service due to convenience, low fees and the market rate of the token.  ▪️ Number of the tokens STM is extremely limited and is 180,000,000. In the future STM will not be released.  ▪️ We plan to create a reserve fund in STM tokens, as well as in the main cryptocurrency and in Fiat currency to maintain liquidity on the service.  ▪️ Each token holder, starting from 1250 STM, will receive a set of privileges and reduced commissions on the STREAMDESK platform.  🔺And the main question-why is it profitable to buy tokens now?  Because now users receive STM tokens at a price much lower than at the time of the service launch, which gives them significant savings when using STREAMITY service.  The cost of one token is set at $0.2 per token, the minimum transaction is 0.1 ETH!  ▶️ You can buy tokens on the project website https://streamity.org

Body: 📌 Fast, reliable, transparent – how STREAMITY changes the market?  If you are reading this post, then you are a part of the cryptocurrency society. You know what Bitcoin and Ethereum are; you may be a NEO or DASH holder; and you definitely are interested in STM tokens and STREAMITY project. Perhaps, you don't quite understand how our platform plans to reform the crypto-market. Now we will tell you!  So, imagine that you need to withdraw ETH and exchange it for dollars. What are the options?  - Use the services of crypto-exchange. But it is important to remember that crypto-exchange trading terminals support the trading function only in the browser window. The terminals themselves are unreliable and do not have enough effective protection against hacking. It is unlikely that you want to be among those who lost their money on exchanges. In addition, with a large load, the terminal may hang and not allow to enter the market. There are also fees for transactions ranging from 0.2 percent to 2 – 3 or even more.  - Withdraw money through the exchange service. It's easier, although the service of exchangers is built on trust – you bring money to the wallet service, it sends us Fiat. The exchange rate is usually not beneficial, and the commission on exchange reach 20 percent. There are also mechanisms for repeatedly charging fees: many platforms for exchanging cryptocurrencies carry out transfers between cryptocurrencies through bitcoin or ether. That is, to exchange NEM for NEO, you will have to buy bitcoin for NEM and only then buy NEO for bitcoin. Commission will be charged on each transaction.  - Use the services of a person who exchange cryptocurrency. Commissions are minimal in this case, but reliability tends to zero… STREAMITY project will change the approach to cryptocurrency exchange! We want to make the process of withdrawal and purchase of cryptocurrencies faster, more convenient and transparent. For this we create a decentralized cryptocurrency exchange platform without intermediaries STREAMDESK. It allows to instantly produce a secure exchange of main cryptocurrencies.  The rate of transactions is based on the analysis of information from the main crypto-exchanges. Thus, STREAMDESK platform provides users with operations at a rate very close to the exchange rate. The security of transactions is provided by smart contracts. Clear and transparent operation of the platform distinguishes it from crypto-exchanges and exchange services.  ☑️ Within the project STREAMITY there will be not only the site STREAMDESK but also some other useful resources from cryptocurrency management's point of view(information-analytical, educational and investment). We do not just want to give the market a tool for convenient withdrawal and input of cryptocurrency – we want to help novice traders to make a profit.  https://streamity.org

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: 📌 Cryptocurrency exchange on existing stocks is a risk  Today, cryptocurrency is one of the components of the digital economy. Millions of dollars have been accumulated on cryptocurrency exchanges. It is not surprising that they become targets of hacker attacks, and some companies do not intentionally fulfill their obligations.  Another difficulty is that the cryptocurrency market is extremely unstable and the exchange service with small fees is quite a risky venture. Companies minimize risks by putting them in the value of the cryptocurrency or in commissions.  The implementation of the project STREAMITY will solve these problems. The idea is to create a p2p-platform, where users find each other and agree on an exchange. As a result, the transaction fee of the system is minimal and user verification and smart-contracts guarantee the security of the transaction.  https://streamity.org

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: ♨️ Exchange cryptocurrency easily, quickly and safely  🔹Do you know that today the average daily volume of cryptocurrency trading is estimated at several billion dollars and this is not the limit?  The market is actively developing and the number of people using cryptocurrency is constantly growing!  🔹 But what if you need to urgently exchange your BTC, ETH, Monero or other currency or withdraw in Fiat?  🔹 How to be when due to the high volatility of the course every second is expensive and the commission can reach sky-high values?  We have made it up! Using Streamity you can make a trade quickly and easily.  Use your crypto wallet, StreamDesk service and any payment system convenient for you to get cash. This is all you need, because our system does not block cryptocurrency or Fiat on the platform - the exchange takes place directly between the seller and the buyer.  A simple interface, a high level of security and a fair deal price, which is calculated as the weighted average price of transactions of leading crypto exchanges at the time of exchange, this is what StreamDesk is.  🔹 Do you want to learn more and become a member of our project?  ☑️ Go to the project site https://streamity.org or ask your questions here and we will be happy to answer them!

From a project standpoint, having a reserve of tokens is reasonable. We have chosen a model of work, in which the tokens remain at the disposal of the project. Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Hello! First of all - The Streamity project includes several unique ideas with high potential. Just imagine: The uniqueness of the information and analytical resource is that any user can add high-quality content to the site! This content will be published after verification by a professional content manager. Of course users will receive specific technical tasks on the site. All you need in order to start working is to download a special form and fill it. Each task will have minimum requirements. We will create a quality and convenient service together, because we make it for ourselves! We will translate our entire library into the most popular languages and it will be available to the entire community anywhere in the world!!!

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Yes, sure Streamdesk is a service designed to exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies, using smart contracts. Streamdesk will also ensure immediate, efficient, and secure mutual exchange of cryptocurrencies for most existing cryptocurrencies in the market. We strive for equal rights of all users interested in buying or selling cryptocurrency without the need for exchange offices, stock exchanges, or any intermediaries. It is super easy -  Register, place orders, and exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies in any way that is convenient for you, and we will take care of your security!  We believe in decentralization. Cryptocurrencies should not be subjected to control by any central authorities. People should be free to manage their finances without external intervention. STREAMITY's fee is as low as 2%. Although we do not deal with fiat currencies, it can be transferred directly between users. Cryptocurrency rates are collected from major exchanges, and will be used to set the market rates for our exchange service.  STREAMDESK service embodies the idea of a truly fair exchange between individuals!

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Local Bitcoins is a bulletin board that matches interested parties in aspecific country. First, this service supports only bitcoins; second, exchange rates are set by the users of the platform; and lastly, there is a lack of secure transactions.   STREAMITY is the first P2P platform ready to protect transactions with smart-contracts. Smart-contracts provide additional security to the cryptocurrency exchange process, in addition to the verification of users. Fair cryptocurrency pricing is an integral part of STREAMITY's services. Rates are calculated in real time, aggregating the average weighted price from major cryptocurrency exchanges. Therefore, STREAMITY users can confidently and securely exchange cryptocurrencies at fair market value. STREAMITY's services allow users to enter the world of cryptocurrency investments seamlessly. Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Thank you for your interest to our project! Here are the steps you should take to purchase cryptocurrency and start trading on STREAMDESK Using  Yandex.Money's  API  for  applications,  we  can  obtain  payment  statuses  from  the  Yandex.Money  server  and  save  users'  data  for  future  payments. Under  this  scenario,  payments  may  be  accepted  in  two  ways:  from Yandex.Money  wallet or from any bank card. Request creation 1) A purchase or sale request is created on STREAMDESK. 2) The  request  may  be  created  by  unauthorized  users;  however,  they  will automatically go through an authorization process. 3) The  following  fields  must  be  filled  out  for  a  purchase  request:  selecting  the payment method, and entering the wallet number. If the user is not authorized, the application  will  show  a  registration  form  with  the  following  parameters:  name, telephone, e-mail, and an agreement for personal data processing. 4) After  the  request  is  created,  the  request  obtains  a  BUY  status  and displayed  on  the STREAMDESK main page. Request acceptance 1) Other  users  may    accept  the  request as  a  Seller  or  Buyer  depending  on  the request type. 2) The following fields must be filled out in the   purchase  request:    selecting  the listed   payment   method    and    entering the  wallet  number.  If    the  user  is  not authorized, the  application will show  the registration   form  with  the  following parameters  to  the  user:  name, telephone,  e-mail,  and  an agreement for personal data processing. 3) After the request is accepted, it obtains a PENDING CONFIRMATION status. 4) The Seller receives a notice that he/she may sell the cryptocurrency. Confirmation and smart contract creation 1) Having obtained the notice, the Seller must confirm the request again. 2) After  the  request  is  confirmed,  it  obtains  the  PENDING  SMART  CONTRACT CREATION status. 3) The  system  checks  parameters  and  availability  of  funds  in  the  Seller’s account, and  creates  a  smart  contract.  The  cryptocurrency  attached to  the smart  contract is  written  off  from  the  Seller’s  account.  The  request  then  obtains  the PENDING PAYMENT status. 4) The  cryptocurrency  is  locked  in  the  smart  contract  (automatically  according  to its  terms  and  conditions)  until  notice  that  the  corresponding  fiat  money  has been credited  to  the  Seller’s  account is verified.  The  request  for  the  smart contract performance is then complete. 5) The  smart  contract  request  expires  (this  occurs  when  the current time exceeds the valid term of the smart contract, which is three hours). 6) After  the  request  obtains  the  PENDING  PAYMENT  status,  the  Buyer  receives  a notice with a payment link. Payment 1) Payment may be made through Yandex.Money, PayPal, Qiwi or other services. (depending on what the user selected). 2) The STREAMDESK  application  works  with  payment  services  through  the HTTPS safe protocol. 3) The STREAMDESK application requests for a right to make a one-time payment to the Seller’s wallet. 3.1)  The  Buyer  logs  into the  payment  service  server  through  OAuth2  secure protocol  and  authorizes  the  one-time  payment  of  the  amount  specified  in  the request. 3.2) OAuth2 protocol makes the authorization secure and convenient. 4) For  transfer  of  funds,  the  payment  service  may  charge  a  commission.  The commission is calculated and indicated when the request is created. 5) After  the  payment  authorization  is  obtained,  the STREAMDESK  application tries  to make the payment. 5.1) If the payment service prohibits the payment, the user receives a proposal to authorize the payment again. 5.2) In case of repeated rejection of payments, the STREAMDESK application assigns a CANCELLED status to the request.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Hi! Great question! First one is that the process Of Buying/Selling Cryptocurrencies is complicated Most P2P platforms work only with BTC and ETH. When buying/selling other cryptocurrencies, first thing to be done is to exchange them for BTC or ETH, and then exchange for fiat money. At each stage user loses funds while paying fees (which can meet the threshold of 10%). The second market problem is that only a Small Number of Cryptocurrencies is Represented on P2P platforms Most P2P platforms accept only ETH and BTC, which prevents the user from quickly creating the desired portfolio of cryptocurrencies. And last one - that Fees are very high when Exchanging Cryptocurrencies for Fiat Money Users all over the world lose up to $ 2.5 billion daily when exchanging crypto-currency for fiat money. Enjoy your day!

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Hello! A first - Streamity is not an internal trading platform. It is powerful informational portal, which includes educational, information-analytical and investment resources,within this project we develop a decentralized P2P platform for cryptocurrency exchange. About payment methods: We have our token (STM) - which you can purchase in BTC, LTC, ETH, ETC, USD, EUR, RUB STREAMITY token (STM) is the key element of the STREAMITY ecosystem. STM constitutes the internal currency of the STREAMITY project. This means that payment for all project services will be made in STMs.  The second question - could you detailed it? What do you mean under "bonus" ? If you participate in the second stage of ico you will get 10% bonus... BONUSPROGRAM STREAMITY offers special discounts depending on the timeliness of the buyer's entrance when purchasing STM. During the pre-ICO, STM will be discounted by 30%. Afterwards, the ICO will consist of two phases: phase one and two. On the first day of phase one, STM will be discounted by 20%. After the first day, phase one, STM will be discounted by 15%. STM will be discounted by 10% during phase two. Furthermore, by purchasing at least 1,250 STM at the pre-ICO, or on the first day of phase one of the ICO, purchasers will receive the STREAMDESK service, provided that purchasers maintain a certain minimum balance in their accounts. For example, if a purchaser invests 1,250 STM at the pre-ICO stage, or on the first day of phase one of the ICO, and keeps 1,250 STEM in their account, the purchaser receives the Platinum package, giving them the right to exchange on the STREAMDESK platform at a 0.5% commission. Similarly, if a purchaser invests 7,500 STM, the purchaser receives the Brilliant package. For a 25,000 STM investment, the purchaser receives the Unlimited package. Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Through the STREAMDESK system you can buy and sell cryptocurrencies. The mechanism for purchase and sale is similar. OAuth means open protocol of authorization. This allows granting limited access to user's protected resources to a third party without needing to transfer a login and password to the third party.  Using Yandex.Money's API for applications, we can obtain payment statuses from the Yandex.Money server and save users' data for future payments. Under this scenario, payments may be accepted in two ways: from Yandex.Money wallet or from any bank card. Request creation 1) A purchase or sale request is created on STREAMDESK. 2) The request may be created by unauthorized users; however, they will automatically go through an authorization process. 3) The following fields must be filled out for a purchase request: selecting the payment method, and entering the wallet number. If the user is not authorized, the application will show a registration form with the following parameters: name, telephone, e-mail, and an agreement for personal data processing. 4) After the request is created, the request obtains a BUY status and displayed on the STREAMDESK main page.  Request acceptance 1) Other users may accept the request as a Seller or Buyer depending on the request type. 2) The following fields must be filled out in the purchase request: selecting the listed payment method and entering the wallet number. If the user is not authorized, the application will show the registration form with the following parameters to the user: name, telephone, e-mail, and an agreement for personal data processing. 3) After the request is accepted, it obtains a PENDING CONFIRMATION status. 4) The Seller receives a notice that he/she may sell the cryptocurrency.  Confirmation and smart contract creation 1) Having obtained the notice, the Seller must confirm the request again. 2) After the request is confirmed, it obtains the PENDING SMART CONTRACT CREATION status. 3) The system checks parameters and availability of funds in the Seller’s account, and creates a smart contract. The cryptocurrency attached to the smart contract is written off from the Seller’s account. The request then obtains the PENDING PAYMENT status. 4) The cryptocurrency is locked in the smart contract (automatically according to its terms and conditions) until notice that the corresponding fiat money has been credited to the Seller’s account is verified. The request for the smart contract performance is then complete. 5) The smart contract request expires (this occurs when the current time exceeds the valid term of the smart contract, which is three hours). 6) After the request obtains the PENDING PAYMENT status, the Buyer receives a notice with a payment link.  Payment 1) Payment may be made through Yandex.Money, PayPal, Qiwi or other services. (depending on what the user selected). 2) The STREAMDESK application works with payment services through the HTTPS safe protocol. 3) The STREAMDESK application requests for a right to make a one-time payment to the Seller’s wallet. 3.1) The Buyer logs into the payment service server through OAuth2 secure protocol and authorizes the one-time payment of the amount specified in the request. 3.2) OAuth2 protocol makes the authorization secure and convenient. 4) For transfer of funds, the payment service may charge a commission. The commission is calculated and indicated when the request is created. 5) After the payment authorization is obtained, the STREAMDESK application tries to make the payment. 5.1) If the payment service prohibits the payment, the user receives a proposal to authorize the payment again. 5.2) In case of repeated rejection of payments, the STREAMDESK application assigns a CANCELLED status to the request.  Smart Contract Performance If the payment is successful (the payment service will indicate a successful transfer of funds), the STREAMDESK application performs the smart contract and assigns the FULFILLED status to the request. The cryptocurrency is then transferred to the Buyer’s account.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Yes! For example we use yandex.money  We need create sale request  on StreamDesk The request may be created by unauthorized users; however, they will automatically go through an authorization process. The following fields must be filled out for a purchase request: selecting the payment method, and entering the wallet number. If the user is not authorized, the application will show a registration form with the following parameters: name, telephone, e-mail, and an agreement for personal data processing. After the request is created, the request obtains a BUY status and displayed on the STREAMDESK main page.  Than someone accept your request (Seller or Buyer depending on the request type) The following fields must be filled out in the purchase request: selecting the Listed payment method and entering the wallet number.  If the user is not authorized, the application will show the registration form with the following parameters to the user: name, telephone, e-mail, and an agreement for personal data processing.  After the request is accepted, it obtains a PENDING CONFIRMATION status. The Seller receives a notice that he/she may sell the cryptocurrency  Confirmation and smart contract creation Having obtained the notice, the Seller must confirm the request again. After the request is confirmed, it obtains the PENDING SMART CONTRACT CREATION status. The system checks parameters and availability of funds in the Seller’s account, and creates a smart contract. The cryptocurrency attached to the smart contract is written off from the Seller’s account. The request then obtains the PENDING PAYMENT status. The cryptocurrency is locked in the smart contract (automatically according to its terms and conditions) until notice that the corresponding fiat money has been credited to the Seller’s account is verified. The request for the smart contract performance is then complete. The smart contract request expires (this occurs when the current time exceeds the valid term of the smart contract, which is three hours). After the request obtains the PENDING PAYMENT status, the Buyer receives a notice with a payment link.  Payment  Payment may be made through Yandex.Money, PayPal, Qiwi or other services. (depending on what the user selected). The STREAMDESK application works with payment services through the HTTPS safe protocol. The STREAMDESK application requests for a right to make a one-time payment to the Seller’s wallet. The Buyer logs into the payment service server through OAuth2 secure protocol and authorizes the one-time payment of the amount specified in the request. OAuth2 protocol makes the authorization secure and convenient. For transfer of funds, the payment service may charge a commission. The commission is calculated and indicated when the request is created. After the payment authorization is obtained, the STREAMDESK application tries to make the payment. If the payment service prohibits the payment, the user receives a proposal to authorize the payment again. In case of repeated rejection of payments, the STREAMDESK application assigns a CANCELLED status to the request.

Body: Yes, sure Streamdesk is a service designed to exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies, using smart contracts. Streamdesk will also ensure immediate, efficient, and secure mutual exchange of cryptocurrencies for most existing cryptocurrencies in the market. We strive for equal rights of all users interested in buying or selling cryptocurrency without the need for exchange offices, stock exchanges, or any intermediaries. It is super easy - Register, place orders, and exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies in any way that is convenient for you, and we will take care of your security!  We believe in decentralization. Cryptocurrencies should not be subjected to control by any central authorities. People should be free to manage their finances without external intervention. STREAMITY's fee is as low as 2%. Although we do not deal with fiat currencies, it can be transferred directly between users. Cryptocurrency rates are collected from major exchanges, and will be used to set the market rates for our exchange service.  STREAMDESK service embodies the idea of a truly fair exchange between individuals!

News portal This section will be created as the aggregator that collects the basic information from crypto-portals, social networks, crypto-companies and developers, it highlights the main aspects and excludes unnecessary information. Market overview The section contains information about market capitalization of cryptocurrencies. This service can be used to evaluate blockchain-companies and cryptocurrencies. This section is the most important for investors as, first of all, you need to know how is one or the other blockchain company placed among its competitors. Also in this section you can find general information about companies, scope of their work, number of tokens, the algorithm of prices collected from major exchange markets in real-time. Each cryptocurrency has a detailed description, rate analysis with technical analysis, recommendations to buy/sell crypto.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Thank you for your interest to our project! Here are the steps you should take to purchase cryptocurrency and start trading on STREAMDESK Using  Yandex.Money's  API  for  applications,  we  can  obtain  payment  statuses  from  the  Yandex.Money  server  and  save  users'  data  for  future  payments. Under  this  scenario,  payments  may  be  accepted  in  two  ways:  from Yandex.Money  wallet or from any bank card. Request creation 1) A purchase or sale request is created on STREAMDESK. 2) The  request  may  be  created  by  unauthorized  users;  however,  they  will automatically go through an authorization process. 3) The  following  fields  must  be  filled  out  for  a  purchase  request:  selecting  the payment method, and entering the wallet number. If the user is not authorized, the application  will  show  a  registration  form  with  the  following  parameters:  name, telephone, e-mail, and an agreement for personal data processing. 4) After  the  request  is  created,  the  request  obtains  a  BUY  status  and displayed  on  the STREAMDESK main page. Request acceptance 1) Other  users  may    accept  the  request as  a  Seller  or  Buyer  depending  on  the request type. 2) The following fields must be filled out in the   purchase  request:    selecting  the listed   payment   method    and    entering the  wallet  number.  If    the  user  is  not authorized, the  application will show  the registration   form  with  the  following parameters  to  the  user:  name, telephone,  e-mail,  and  an agreement for personal data processing. 3) After the request is accepted, it obtains a PENDING CONFIRMATION status. 4) The Seller receives a notice that he/she may sell the cryptocurrency. Confirmation and smart contract creation 1) Having obtained the notice, the Seller must confirm the request again. 2) After  the  request  is  confirmed,  it  obtains  the  PENDING  SMART  CONTRACT CREATION status. 3) The  system  checks  parameters  and  availability  of  funds  in  the  Seller’s account, and  creates  a  smart  contract.  The  cryptocurrency  attached to  the smart  contract is  written  off  from  the  Seller’s  account.  The  request  then  obtains  the PENDING PAYMENT status. 4) The  cryptocurrency  is  locked  in  the  smart  contract  (automatically  according  to its  terms  and  conditions)  until  notice  that  the  corresponding  fiat  money  has been credited  to  the  Seller’s  account is verified.  The  request  for  the  smart contract performance is then complete. 5) The  smart  contract  request  expires  (this  occurs  when  the current time exceeds the valid term of the smart contract, which is three hours). 6) After  the  request  obtains  the  PENDING  PAYMENT  status,  the  Buyer  receives  a notice with a payment link. Payment 1) Payment may be made through Yandex.Money, PayPal, Qiwi or other services. (depending on what the user selected). 2) The STREAMDESK  application  works  with  payment  services  through  the HTTPS safe protocol. 3) The STREAMDESK application requests for a right to make a one-time payment to the Seller’s wallet. 3.1)  The  Buyer  logs  into the  payment  service  server  through  OAuth2  secure protocol  and  authorizes  the  one-time  payment  of  the  amount  specified  in  the request. 3.2) OAuth2 protocol makes the authorization secure and convenient. 4) For  transfer  of  funds,  the  payment  service  may  charge  a  commission.  The commission is calculated and indicated when the request is created. 5) After  the  payment  authorization  is  obtained,  the STREAMDESK  application tries  to make the payment. 5.1) If the payment service prohibits the payment, the user receives a proposal to authorize the payment again. 5.2) In case of repeated rejection of payments, the STREAMDESK application assigns a CANCELLED status to the request.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: No, it's not the same platform. In  contrast  to  our  competitors,  STREAMITY  is  the  first  P2P  platform  ready  to protect transactions with smart-contracts. Fair  cryptocurrency  pricing  is  an  integral  part  of STREAMITY's  services.  Rates are  calculated  in  real  time,  aggregating  the  average  weighted  price  from major cryptocurrency exchanges. Our advantages: · The STREAMITY project is a one-stop shop for cryptocurrency services; · The  development  of  STREAMITY  services,  and  the  influx  of  new  users, will create a strong and steady demand for STM; · STM   will  be  available  on major cryptocurrency  exchanges, allowing users and investors to trade instantly; · Due to STREAMDESK's convenience, low commissions, and efficient market rates,  STREAMDESK  allows  for  economical  conversion  between  fiat currency and  STM; · The  manipulation risk of  STM  rates  is  minimized  due  to  its  reserve fund; and · Each  user  holding  more  than  1250  STM  will  receive  a  set  of  privileges, including  lower  commissions on  the STREAMDESK platform.

Author: trespiclof
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Woow! What is StreamDesk?

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Let me explain) StreamDesk is a P2P platform where both parties to a transaction are individuals. There is no comparison between StreamDesk and conventional financial institutions such as banks or stock exchanges, as fiat currencies are transferred directly between individuals. StreamDesk is the innovative P2P platform based on the technology of blockchain, attractive due to its safety and favorable terms of transactions. The whole process is remote, which allows users to manage their time more effectively.

Author: trespiclof
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: And could you describe the StreamDesk application, please))

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Yes, sure Streamdesk is a service designed to exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies, using smart contracts. Streamdesk will also ensure immediate, efficient, and secure mutual exchange of cryptocurrencies for most existing cryptocurrencies in the market. We strive for equal rights of all users interested in buying or selling cryptocurrency without the need for exchange offices, stock exchanges, or any intermediaries. It is super easy - Register, place orders, and exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies in any way that is convenient for you, and we will take care of your security!  We believe in decentralization. Cryptocurrencies should not be subjected to control by any central authorities. People should be free to manage their finances without external intervention. STREAMITY's fee is as low as 2%. Although we do not deal with fiat currencies, it can be transferred directly between users. Cryptocurrency rates are collected from major exchanges, and will be used to set the market rates for our exchange service.  STREAMDESK service embodies the idea of a truly fair exchange between individuals!

Author: kolfedinew
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: What is actually KYC? Should I pass it?

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: The KYC (Know Your Customer) procedure  includes  identification  of  financial  beneficiaries, and beneficial  owners,  as  they  are  customers  of  financial  institutions (which  encompasses cryptocurrency exchange services). Strict  compliance  of  KYC  policies  protects  financial  institutions  and  their customers from suspicious money and transaction activities. As  transaction security  is one of the  main priorities of the STREAMITY ecosystem, we  must  identify  our  customers  and  verify  their  provided  information.  In exceptional  cases,  where a high risk customer is identified,  STREAMITY  reserves the right to reject access to the exchange platform without giving a reason. For customer identification, copies of the following documents are required: (a) page  of  the  international  passport with  the  photo,  indication of the full  name,nationality, date and place of birth, date of issue and expiration of the passport, its number, country issuing the passport and signature or a copy of another document (ID card/ driver’s license) containing the above information; (b) invoice  for  utility  services  (for  example,  electricity,  telephone,  etc.)  or  a bank statement indicating the date (not earlier than three months before the date of 27 provision of the bank statement), registered  name, permanent place of residence and mailing address; (c) a copy of their bank card; (d) a selfie in which the face and passport of the customer can be clearly seen; and (e) copies  of  constituent  documents  (account  identification  for  legal entities). STREAMITY  also  reserves  the  right  to  rely  on  the  identification  carried  out  by STREAMITY  partners  (payment  systems)  or  engage  third  party  specialized services (CIVIC, IDnowIdent, etc.) to carry out its KYC procedure. To ensure mutual confidence, STREAMITY  guarantees  its  best  efforts  to  keep customer information confidential.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Yes, sure Streamdesk is a service designed to exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies, using smart contracts. Streamdesk will also ensure immediate, efficient, and secure mutual exchange of cryptocurrencies for most existing cryptocurrencies in the market. We strive for equal rights of all users interested in buying or selling cryptocurrency without the need for exchange offices, stock exchanges, or any intermediaries. It is super easy -  Register, place orders, and exchange cryptocurrencies for fiat currencies in any way that is convenient for you, and we will take care of your security!  We believe in decentralization. Cryptocurrencies should not be subjected to control by any central authorities. People should be free to manage their finances without external intervention. STREAMITY's fee is as low as 2%. Although we do not deal with fiat currencies, it can be transferred directly between users. Cryptocurrency rates are collected from major exchanges, and will be used to set the market rates for our exchange service.  STREAMDESK service embodies the idea of a truly fair exchange between individuals!

Author: trespiclof
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Thank you! Our competitors - Local Bitcoins, Challengy, Qvolta - Lets explain the differ from them:  Local Bitcoins is a bulletin board that matches interested parties in a specific country. This service supports only bitcoins  and exchange rates are set by the users of the platform. And there is a lack of secure transactions.  Changelly is a platform that supports a few dozens of cryptocurrencies.  But users can buy cryptocurrency for US dollars, they are not allowed to sell cryptocurrency for fiat money.  About security: the security of a deal is guaranteed only by the credibility of the team. This assurance is suspect, as the security technology is not transparent. Qvolta is a new service created in 2017 and have raised its funds via an ICO. To date, this platform is still in a “test mode”. Although this service states that customers can use different payment methods, it only supports Bitcoin and Ethereum. They claims that their security system will protect its accounts and transactions. However, the development of this platform is still in progress. There is a lack of technical description of its processes.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Thank you for your question, primarily P2P cryptocurrency exchange services. You have already known that P2P solutions are far from being perfect:  Local Bitcoins is a bulletin board that matches interested parties in a specific country. First, this service supports only bitcoins; second, exchange rates are set by the users of the platform; third, there is a lack of secure transactions.  Changelly is a platform that supports a few dozens of cryptocurrencies. But users can buy cryptocurrency for US dollars, they are not allowed to sell cryptocurrency for fiat money. Security: the security of a deal is guaranteed only by the credibility of the team. This assurance is suspect, as the security technology is not transparent.  Qvolta is a new service created in 2017 and have raised its funds via an ICO. To date, this platform is still in a “test mode”. Although this service states that customers can use different payment methods, it only supports Bitcoin and Ethereum. Qvolta claims that their security system will protect its accounts and transactions. However, the development of this platform is still in progress. It is unclear how smart-contracts will be used within this platform, as there is a lack of technical description of its processes.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Hey! Thank you for a Great question! First of all, StreamDesk is P2P cryptocurrency exchange services. So i will provide you our unique features which made us stand out from other P2P solutions   here we go: - Local Bitcoins is a bulletin board that matches interested parties in a specific country. First, this service supports only bitcoins; second, exchange rates are set by the users of the platform; and lastly, but most important - there is a lack of secure transactions!  - Changelly is a platform that supports a few dozens of cryptocurrencies. First - users can buy cryptocurrency for US dollars, but cant sell cryptocurrency for fiat money. Second, the security of a deal is guaranteed only by the credibility of the team. (its mean that the security) technology is not transparent.  - Qvolta is a new service created in 2017 and have raised its funds via an ICO. To date, this platform is still in a “test mode”. This service states that customers can use different payment methods (nowadays supports only Bitcoin and Ethereum). Qvolta claims that their security system will protect its accounts and transactions. However, the development of this platform is still in progress. It is unclear how smart-contracts will be used within this platform, as there is a lack of technical description of its processes.  In contrast to our competitors, STREAMITY is the first P2P platform ready to protect transactions with smart-contracts.  - Smart-contracts provide additional security to the cryptocurrency exchange process, in addition to the verification of users. - Fair cryptocurrency pricing is an integral part of STREAMITY's services. Rates are calculated in real time, aggregating the average weighted price from major cryptocurrency exchanges. - Users can confidently and securely exchange cryptocurrencies at fair market value. - Services allow users to enter the world of cryptocurrency investments seamlessly. - We expect the majority of our customers to be active users of on-line payments systems. - Although these users are generally familiar with on-line payment systems and cryptocurrencies, they require a higher standard for security than initial cryptocurrency enthusiasts.  As the cryptocurrency markets expand, platforms, such as STREAMITY, are poised to service the next wave of cryptocurrency users. Enjoy your reading!

Author: Partnerra
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Cool review on ICOCrunch  🏤Streamity – https://icocrunch.io/ico/streamity/ What – Decentralized P2P cryptocurrency exchange When – Mar 12-25 (phase 1), Apr 16-29 (phase 2) Rating – 4.3👍  Idea & Token Nowadays there is no cryptocurrency exchange service allowing converting cryptocurrency in fiat money fast and safely. Moreover, they are complicated, illegal and set huge commissions. Streamity is aiming to resolve it. The Streamity project consists of two main components: – StreamDesk This is a P2P platform for smart contract cryptocurrency exchange managed with a decentralized application developed by Streamity. The platform provides the service of fast and secure cryptocurrency-to-fiat exchange with minimal commissions (from 0% to 2%). What is important – the operations will be performed without the need for a centralized third party. Currently most of exchange operations are conducted on centralized exchanges which may lead to issues with regulatory authorities and blocking users’ accounts. The P2P technology eliminates suchlike situations. – A free portal about cryptocurrency The portal will provide lots of information about cryptocurrency - analytical, educational and investment resources, including market review, news, ideas, blogs, articles, knowledge base, investment statistics, ICO recommendations. The portal will be made by community and for the community, and it will be free of charge. Streamity token (STM) is an ERC-20 token that will be used within the entire ecosystem as a payment method for all services offered by the project, including the P2P cryptocurrency exchange. The full supply of tokens is limited to 186 million, 100 million tokens will be sold on the ICO. On the first day of the ICO you will get 20% discount, days 2-14 – 15% discount, and 10% - during phase 2 of the ICO. Token distribution – 70% for ICO, 25% for the team, 3% for the rewards program, and 2% for the advisors and partners.  Team The team consists of 16 specialists, most of which are experienced software developers. Add here professionals in blockchain technology, marketing, traders, investors, and Streamity’s CEO Vladislav Kuznetsov who has more than 10 years of experience in business and asset management at the stock market. And they are still looking for new members in the team. The team doesn’t look very experienced in cryptocurrency market and blockchain, they are rather excellent specialists in other spheres who were inspired by the blockchain technology. This is partly compensated by advisors, more experienced in blockchain. All in all they have 10 advisors and one company-partner (BBS PTE, Best Business Solutions).  Summary The idea is pretty good, since the market still needs a cryptocurrency exchange that could be fast, secure, reliable, cheap, and independent from third parties. Though the project is still in its beginning, it seems that Streamity has all the necessary ingredients to bring it to success – a good idea, inspired team, clear whitepaper, and desire to make the cryptocurrency market a bit better and more comfortable. Anyway, don’t forget about other ICOs trying to achieve the same goal, because this project is not the first attempt to improve cryptocurrency exchanges.  Yet another attempt to resolve old shortcomings of today’s cryptocurrency exchanges – slow and expensive transactions, and necessity to include third parties in the processes. Add here a pleasant bonus in the form of free informational portal for the community and you’ll get the picture of Streamity.

Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Reasons to buy STM token A unique service "StreamDesk". We develop a unique service for the profitable purchase/sale of cryptocurrency under the credible security of smart contracts and payment systems all over the world.  Buy and sell cryptocurrency without commissions. Early investors are privileged to use such functions of StreamDesk service as purchase/sale of cryptocurrency without commissions.  Legitimacy. Streamity PTE. LTD. is registered in Singapore. Investors can officially purchase tokens regardless of their location. Our company supports partnership with the largest payment systems.  STM token is in the center of Streamity ecosystem. STM tokens are used for the purchase of services within Streamity ecosystem. As more services are launched within Streamity platform, the more tokens are in demand.  Minimal risks. There are minimal chances to manipulate STM token rate as they are protected with STM token and fiat money reserve funds.  Active team. Active and well-coordinated team of highly professional developers is ready to bring ideas to life.

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: In contrast to our competitors, STREAMITY is the first P2P platform ready to protect transactions with smart-contracts. Smart-contracts provide additional security to the cryptocurrency exchange process in addition to the verification of users. Fair price for a deal is an important part of STREAMITY functions. It is calculated in real time as an average weighted price of the major cryptocurrency exchange markets’ deals. Therefore, STREAMITY users can be sure they make their deals at a fair price with maximal security

Body: The StreamDesk platform does not work with banks. The information on transactions is not usually enciphered and is open and available. Banks, tax, judicial and other state or private authorities cannot influence transactions of any participants of the payment system. The cryptocurrency transfer is irreversible: nobody can cancel, block, dispute or carry out a transaction forcibly (without a private key).

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: New Age of P2P Cryptocurrency to Fiat Exchange and the Reverse with Streamity  Streamity, a P2P platform that allows a faster low fee exchanges of all the major cryptocurrencies to fiat currencies and vice versa. Streamity deploys a smart contract run system to achieve absolute transaction security. The platform promises a new approach to cryptocurrency exchanges to fiat currencies by incorporating an industry standard smart contract powered security feature. Streamity design ensures a secure, user friendly P2P cryptocurrency exchange design to suit current and future user demands.  Streamity will change the way everybody around the world interacts with cryptocurrencies by simplifying conversions of cryptocurrencies to fiat money and vice versa. The platform has developed a fast and secured transaction channel which significantly reduces the transaction time to just a few minutes. To ensure system security and protect its users from fraud Streamity implements a Know Your Customer (KYC) and Anti Money Laundering (AML) policies.  Read more: https://coinidol.com/new-age-of-p2p-cryptocurrency-to-fiat-exchange-with-streamity/

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Hi, thank you for your question! Our company is already registered in Singapore. Our activities are going to be absolutely legal. Commission from 0 to 2% will depend on the package of benefits you choose. It means that you won't have any benifits if you do not buy a package and your commission will stand at 2%. If you want to learn more, check out the monetization section in the Whitepaper. There are no other commissions! Here are the main stages of the process: Now on the coinmarketcap Ethereum costs 450$, you make a request to buy one ETH; while you directly transfer money to the seller, cryptocurrency is blocked in a smart contract. You recieve one ETH minus 2%commission. That's all! Everything is so easy! If you have a considerable turnover then buy a benifit package and exchange cryptocurrency without commissions!

Author: boranes
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: I don't understand something. You are doing ICO for decentralized exchange and I read in first post that you are in talks with exchanges. Why would any exchange list token of their competition and why do you need other exchange to list this token? When you launch exchange you can list token there, right?

Author: Streamity
Title: [ANN] STREAMITY ICO --->Decentralized cryptocurrency exchange<---
Body: Thank you for your question! We do not create an exchange market, it is the p2p platform for cryptocurrency exchange, where the exchange will take place directly between people and we will guarantee the security of these operations with smart contracts. At the meantime our token will be traded openly on exchange markets, which allows to buy STM token easily on our platform and then transfer it to an exchange market. Currently it is very difficult to transfer fiat money to exchange markets, it is very expensive and takes a lot of time! Also the majority of exchange markets do not have a license and their users are risking to lose their funds. And we can solve this problem!
